reviews.text: Just your average chained sushi place. Food not bad. Place not bad. Good for a quick meal.

Come for casual lunch on rainy Saturday. Quite crowded. Sushi feeds our imagination well of being in Japan! But do not expect very high quality food but good value. Genki member enjoys points discount and afternoon tea set starts at 2:30 instead of 3 pm. Nice!

Loose rice by machine made sushi. Don’t dip it into soy sauce plate or it falls & soak excess soy souce.Wrong delivery of 3 plates of sushi. Staff tried to refill hot pot but forgot to bring it back. Are they all in holiday mood?
genki sushi in banyan mall has good customer service and their lunch menu is good value too
Our go to place for cheap fast sushi

reviews.text: 服務員看上去只有2至3人，可能工作繁忙態度不是太好。
店舖頗大，但只得2至3個waitresses。客人較多時，連基本服務都欠奉。食品方面，套餐中手卷的紫菜是軟的，但單叫手卷的紫菜是脆的！真現實，有奸商潛質。
服務態度較差，黑面較其他分店多
